sequenceDiagram
  actor U as User
  participant W as Web
  participant A as API
  participant T as Temporal
  participant C as Connector Workers
  participant P as PostgreSQL
  participant G as Graph Projection
  participant M as AI Gateway
  participant S as Simulation
  participant J as Jira
  U->>W: Seed and synchronize demo tenant
  W->>A: Start reconciliation
  A->>T: Durable sync workflow
  T->>C: Fetch allowlisted GitHub and Jira metadata
  C->>P: Upsert observations claims and outbox
  P-->>G: Rebuildable projection events
  U->>W: Why is launch at risk?
  W->>A: Authorized question
  A->>M: Permission-trimmed evidence and graph tools
  M-->>U: Cited answer or abstention
  U->>W: Confirm scenario assumptions
  W->>S: Seeded PERT Monte Carlo run
  S-->>U: p50 p80 p95 critical path and sensitivity
  U->>W: Draft remediation
  W->>A: Exact Jira preview
  A-->>U: Immutable payload awaiting two approvals
  U->>A: First approval
  actor V as Second approver
  V->>A: Second approval
  A->>T: Idempotent action workflow
  T->>J: Upsert remediation issue once
  J-->>A: Provider receipt
  A-->>U: Audit and rollback option

